;O:8:"stdClass":7:{s:2:"id";s:2:"12";s:7:"section";s:1:"0";s:4:"name";s:12:"About Course";s:7:"summary";s:767:"Are you prepared to help your team navigate the complexities of AI? In this course, join author and C-suite leader Laysha Ward as she outlines essential human-centered leadership skills to help you lead your team effectively in the age of AI. Through practical strategies, hands-on practice, and learning exercises, Laysha demonstrates how to lead through ambiguity and complexity, communicate with intent, and design workflows that optimize both human and AI capabilities. By the end of this course, you’ll be prepared to drive ethical, resilient, and purpose-driven transformation across your organization.

